      "properties": { "text": "" },
      "widgets_values": ["VIBRANT vs FREQUENCY (comparison)\n\nThe same image is sent to the default (frequency) extractor and three Vibrant modes: vibrant / muted / dark_vibrant. Compare the four swatch strips.\n\n- Frequency ranks colors by how COMMON they are (often a dull background leads).\n- Vibrant scores colors by saturation/lightness, so striking accents surface first.\n\nTry the other modes too (light_vibrant / light_muted / dark_muted). Whichever palette you prefer wires into Palette->Global JSON the same way - just move the link from your chosen extractor."],
