    "note": "VIBRANT vs FREQUENCY: the same reference is sent to the default (frequency-ranked) extractor and three Vibrant Extractor modes (vibrant / muted / dark_vibrant). Compare the four swatch strips: the frequency extractor leads with the most COMMON color (often a dull background), while vibrant modes surface striking accent colors first. Whichever palette you prefer wires into Palette->Global JSON identically -- here the 'vibrant' output is carried onward as an example (rewire link 9 from a different extractor to pick another). Try the other modes (light_vibrant / light_muted / dark_muted) on the Vibrant nodes too. ShowText is OPTIONAL (ComfyUI-Custom-Scripts)."
